The <strong>Community Activation Coordinator</strong> is the primary caretaker of the GOOD community,&nbsp;with a focus on Active Members. He/she should be the site&rsquo;s most active member, know all of&nbsp;our most active users by name, and active individuals and organizations should know him/her&nbsp;by name. Through site activity and informed by analytics, he/she should know influencers in key&nbsp;sub-communities on the site and should engage with them regularly through Follows, Comments,&nbsp;and direct communication. He/she will work closely with the Programming team to strategize and&nbsp;coordinate community involvement in Big Win campaigns.</p>
